{"id":303338,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-福建冤民王尾珠在中南海撒传单被拘留（/","date":"2013-07-12T09:32:54Z","modified":"2013-07-12T09:32:54Z","title":"维权网 | 福建冤民王尾珠在中南海撒传单被拘留（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙强报道）深感没了活路的福建三明女冤民王尾珠，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>又被北京府右街派出所行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天，原因是她在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日下午</span><span>和福建陈贞西、杨小华、谢就发、杨明梅夫妻、苏树美、黄金英夫妻、陈春英、苏春治、蔡淑敏、王琼、杨示谷、谢宝治等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>冤民一起到北京中南海抛洒传单（自己的控告材料），要向习近平主席陈情诉冤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>非常巧合的是就在去年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，诉告无门的王尾珠因进京寻找著名艺术 家艾未未 先生帮助维权，被当地公安强行遣送回福州，先拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天后再处劳教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王尾珠自解除劳教恢复自由身后，就抱着惨死的儿子相框，依然执着地踏上进京为儿鸣冤的上访征程。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>闯北京美使馆被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>只身到天安门广场撒传单被抓被囚禁在马家楼；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>又孤身一人到美使馆前喊冤叫屈再次被囚马家楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王尾珠从儿子被几个暴徒活活打死后开始，她的遭遇，她的命运堪比永州上访妈妈唐慧悲惨百倍！可诉告无门，加上她所控告的充斥黑司法、无正义、没法律的当地警方还在屡屡报复迫害她，更让她冤上加冤，感到绝望。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>闯中南海撒传单的福建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>名冤民中，王尾珠、杨明梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名冤民被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天，苏春治、谢宝治</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名冤民被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天，其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>名冤民送到马家楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-A_uqX25nGNw/Ud-RqGS2pxI/AAAAAAAAlJc/kLvse8P7mZ8/s1600/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130711212143.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-A_uqX25nGNw/Ud-RqGS2pxI/AAAAAAAAlJc/kLvse8P7mZ8/s320/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130711212143.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[10619,16910,14115]}